<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">Site News - <font align="left" class="newsDate">7:41 PM PDT</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText"><p>Earlier this evening we held another fantastic chat with the devs at EverQuest, and there were some great questions from the community:</p><blockquote><p><font color="#0000FF">&lt;Destinova&gt;</font> *Dexar* Will there be instanced group missions in the new expansion?<br><font color="#800000"><strong>&lt;Rashere&gt; </strong></font>Sure will. We've tried to cover the gamut of play styles with this expansion, so it includes both static zone content and group-based missions.</p></blockquote><p>For that and more, be sure to check out the full log <a href="http://eq.stratics.com/content/hoclogs/20070718.php"><strong>her</a></strong>, and join us for our next chat with the developers!  Watch our news for the next scheduled date!</td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText"><div align="center">[ <a href="">Comment on this article</a> ]</div></td></tr>


