    <td align="left" valign="middle" class="newsSubject"><img src="/images/clear.gif" width="9" height="10">A Tour of Everquest: The Buried Sea!</td><td class="newsSubject"><div align="right"><a class="comment" href="#top"><img src="/images/news/top.gif" border="0" alt="Return to Top"></a><img src="/images/clear.gif" width="9" height="10"><a class="comment" href="mailto:eqnews@stratics.com?subject=News"><img src="/images/news/submitnews.gif" border="0" alt="Submit News!"></a><img src="/images/clear.gif" width="9" height="10"><a class="comment" href=""><img src="/images/news/forums.gif" border="0" alt="Comment on this article"></a><img src="/images/clear.gif" width="9" height="10"></div></td>
