<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="3" valign="top">   
<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">Interviews and Reviews - <font align="left" class="newsDate">12:05 PM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText"><p>Do you ever feel like your game needs a little more content? You know, that feeling you get when you are up against your 10th NPC that is named "Mr. Johnson" and aren't really sure why you are killing him again. Fear no more fellow gamers, for your solution is here: EverQuest the Buried Sea!</p><blockquote>You are one of the many players of EverQuest, and are about to embark on a new adventure. This game has had many expansions, with each one providing new content and new stories for adventures. The Buried Sea is another phenomenal experience for players to love.</blockquote><p>EverQuest has always been chock FULL of content, and they continue their tradition with their newest expansion The Buried Sea. Follow with Stratics on an <a href = "http://eq.stratics.com/content/features/exclusives/buriedsea/buriedseatour.php">Exclusive Tour</a> of this amazing expansion.</p></td></tr>
