<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">GeneralNews - <font align="left" class="newsDate">5:30 PM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText"><p>Earlier this evening we held a House of Commons Developer Chat with the developer team from <a href="http://everquest.station.sony.com/" target="_blank">EverQuest</a>. The topic was their upcoming expansion: The Buried Sea.  Many questions were asked and answered such as:  </p><blockquote>    <p><font color="#0000FF">Calelena</font> *Wycca* Will we be seeing some in-game events to launch TBS? Ie something lore related that explains it, and something that can be fun?</p>    <p><font color="#800000">Vahlar</font> Yes, live events will unfold as we get closer to the release of the expansion. What you will see is something world-changing that we've never done before. I think it's fun as heck. For you it will be mysterious. There is a lot of lore around these events, but it will be up to players to investigate and unravel it.</p></blockquote><p>To read the full log, please go <a href="http://eq.stratics.com/content/hoclogs/20070124.php">here</a>. And we hope to see you at our next EverQuest Developer Chat; Check back here for that upcoming date!</p></td></tr>
